// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-0013 — Mass File Rename (safepay)
// Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 6ba9d28b-bc60-5187-8957-81031570902c

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
